/year) typically required unless scholarship or sponsor alternative applies."},{"q":"What is Key authority for this service?","a":"Polish Embassy/Consulate in India · VFS Global Poland · Migration Department (www.gov.pl) after arrival"},{"q":"What is After approval for this service?","a":"Enter Poland; register address; apply for temporary residence permit at Migration Department (www.gov.pl) within visa validity."},{"q":"Is Admission from recognised Polish institution required?","a":"Admission from recognised Polish institution is typically required."},{"q":"Is Proof of funds (€800/month (verify UdSC amount)) required?","a":"Apply early—processing takes weeks"},{"q":"Is Proof of funds or financial proof required?","a":"€9,600+/year or equivalent with 3–6 month bank history"},{"q":"Is Health insurance (travel + statutory) required?","a":"Assess whether Health insurance (travel + statutory) is satisfied for this case."},{"q":"Is Motivation letter and CV required?","a":"Motivation letter and CV is typically required."},{"q":"Is Language proficiency (as required) required?","a":"Polish or English per program"},{"q":"Is Valid passport required?","a":"Valid passport is typically required."},{"q":"What is the Processing time?","a":"6–12w — After complete file complete"},{"q":"What is the Government fee?","a":"€75 — + proof of funds required living funds"},{"q":"What is the Our approval rate?","a":"88% — ~74% benchmark"},{"q":"What is the Required docs?","a":"15 — + proof of funds €9,600+"},{"q":"What is the Consultancy fee?","a":"See fee tab — + govt & third-party"},{"q":"What if the client has Proof of funds insufficient?","a":"Open blocked account or show €9,600+ equivalent with 3–6 month bank history before embassy slot"},{"q":"Why is Proof of funds insufficient a problem?","a":"Proof of funds below €800/month (verify UdSC amount) or inconsistent bank history."},{"q":"What if the client has Insufficient proof of funds?","a":"Open proof of funds at approved bank for ful